   - catalogue_keys from catalogues_template.csv
   - generator_keys from generators_template.csv
   - note_type_keys from template/note_types_template.csv
3. Check all references:
   - variables.task_key -> tasks.task_id
   - variables.enum_ref -> enums.enum_key (if not empty)
   - variables.catalogue_ref -> catalogues.catalogue_key (if not empty)
