   - tasks.note_type_keys (comma-separated) -> note_types.note_type_key
   - variables.catalogue_ref -> catalogues.catalogue_key (if not empty)
   - variables.generator_ref -> generators.generator_key (if not empty)
   - variables.note_type_ref -> note_types.note_type_key (if not empty)
4. Report broken references
```

